heading: Guulrahn Slums Dungeon Guide
content: Guulrahn Slums features the absolute top tier Necromancer aspect, . We would recommend avoiding this dungeon for Nightmare Dungeons, as it features two unfavorable monster families and the dreaded slay all enemies objective. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
